JOHANNESBURG - A pedestrian has died after he was struck by a vehicle on the M1 near the Glenhove off-ramp. Paramedics said that the victim was attempting to cross the highway on Sunday night. It's understood that he suffered fatal injuries and was declared dead when paramedics arrived. Emer-G-Med paramedics said that a 14-year-old passenger from the vehicle suffered moderate injuries and was taken to hospital.